channel.title: File error FR_NOT_ENABLED
channel.description:
hi there, pretty new to axoloti but this has been showing up in my console since day 1, happens every time i make a patch go live.
The full error message "file error: FR_NOT_ENABLED, filename:"/untitled""
Any ideas what this is and how i can fix it ? thanks

item.title: File error FR_NOT_ENABLED
item.dc:creator: @johannes johannes
item.description:
@johannes wrote:

It means that it can't access a micro-sdcard, most likely because there is no micro-sdcard inserted.
It's harmless, you can safely ignore it.
This will be gone in the next version.

Read full topic
